! https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/font_configuration
Xft.autohint: 0
ft.lcdfilter: lcddefault
Xft.hintstyle: hintslight
Xft.hinting: 1
Xft.antialias: 1
Xft.rgba: rgb

